{"tid":339152,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好朋友真係無可能變戀人？","createTime":"2017-07-28T19:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T04:46:12.000Z","uid":38772,"like":21,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a609218689a7d1f4442fc62dac9dceb45bd05aa4","tid":339152,"uid":38772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:51:04.000Z","msg":"同個女仔都識左幾年 想追佢但又怕無左個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴絲們點睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：放膽去追 搏盡無悔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：放棄la 朋友 別引誘"},{"pid":"2a956c3245ef6c5aff545f3a1260402f11356554","tid":339152,"uid":130732,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T20:02:07.000Z","msg":"我依家既處境都同你一樣<br />\n識左個女仔由中學識到依家都有5年到<br />\n佢都知我鐘意佢 但從來冇反抗過 <br />\n我都努力追緊 <br />\n你自己諗下過左20年之後會唔會仲好似依家咁friend? <br />\n冇可能 到時各有各家庭 你後悔都無謂<br />\n而家追左 可能你第時就係佢老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己諗啦巴打"},{"pid":"d55a9f3ca273b47983dd697a11fbd511ea180ede","tid":339152,"uid":75694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T20:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去馬啦 再等就變早霸王咁"},{"pid":"65fd576e115c9b7d01b744b7469eeb6ba2187b64","tid":339152,"uid":76584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T21:09:02.000Z","msg":"戀無可戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3026f8eb86facebfbeb7c1a19cc55e6a32a9570f","tid":339152,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"有火花就得"},{"pid":"31a8cce54c6d0a967fcbaed5376fcd88390794b0","tid":339152,"uid":46818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"我係成功例子"},{"pid":"862e3b028646fe9f30183f8c45956c17f7f6a678","tid":339152,"uid":54994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"我都遇番個EX<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢依家開始成日同我講佢唔開心既野，其實算係CLOSE左好多<br />\n<br />\n我都打算追番佢，所以想做就唔好等，至少你努力過。"},{"pid":"5c25a929dae278fe8bd776e3fac586563e928023","tid":339152,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae4451fd8a785f3db780c419140e15a7587632f8","tid":339152,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"總之覺得啱就去啦<br />\n唔好到咗八年後先後悔"},{"pid":"bd2ddcc63dbeb15741b01baecbc028b4de7d7e2f","tid":339152,"uid":96402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"要諗清楚接唔接受到分手後大家係永遠嘅陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過比best frd鍾意 <br />\n一開始拒絕因為唔想分手後失去佢 <br />\n因為太珍惜佢 <br />\n結果後尾都係違背唔到自己想同佢一齊嘅諗法 <br />\n分手後應該係出世為止最辛苦最痛嘅一段時間 <br />\n從此陌路人 各自出國讀書 冇再聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b12fdb0c9eddf5e2ba251e8422557e0a4829b4","tid":339152,"uid":28536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"共你親到無可親密後 便知友誼萬歲是盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dc53921110489ea0baa0481b5d0859a30e4973","tid":339152,"uid":128964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過，識左幾年，三個月唔到就散<br />\n你自己諗</blockquote><br />\n有無後悔到？"},{"pid":"2e2e9e74ed253be1bffbf51678cfc25d5092433f","tid":339152,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec0c239be097370835df5b8a8d51e2ac8012bbf","tid":339152,"uid":29717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10年fd,我就係成功例子"},{"pid":"18ab6370c4c01917d3d7d675dbbcdbb46b60a4d5","tid":339152,"uid":63923,"like":2,"di